FILE-FORMAT
===========
read old-school "amb"-files
  as "ambix extended" files with a conversion-matrix

helper-library
==============
library for matrix operations related to libambix
- find a good name for it
- generate standard conversion matrices, namely for 
-- common channel orderings
-- common normalization schemes (semi-normalized and normalized)
-- Furse-Malham
- analysis of existing matrices

UTILITIES
=========
ambix-jrec
  utility to record ambix files via jack

ambix-jplay
  utility to play back ambix files via jack



